					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5381322#post-3753671</guid>
				<title>+150!</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5381322/scp-3340#post-3753671</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 30 Mar 2018 09:03:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ayers</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1856789</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thank you guys, I never expected to do this well.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[+]&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;use&nbsp;this&nbsp;post&nbsp;as&nbsp;an&nbsp;excuse&nbsp;to&nbsp;do&nbsp;something&nbsp;I&nbsp;should&nbsp;have&nbsp;done&nbsp;a&nbsp;long&nbsp;time&nbsp;ago.</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[-]&nbsp;The&nbsp;'Thank&nbsp;Yous!'</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>This would not have been made possible without the kind words and criticisms from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1558990&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522400625" alt="Leveritas" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1558990)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" >Leveritas</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magellani" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3670353&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522400625" alt="Magellani" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3670353)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magellani" >Magellani</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toa-vine" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2023146&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522400625" alt="Toa_Vine" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2023146)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toa-vine" >Toa_Vine</a></span>. I can't thank you guys enough.</p> <p>After reading <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2712">SCP-2712</a> and <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/patterns">Patterns</a>, I <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">ripped them off completely</span> had this idea.</p> <p>And a huge thank you to everyone who left criticism in this discussion thread. As my first skip on the mainpage, I don't want to make the same mistakes again.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
